OR // MASKEDHELP</p><div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px\"><span class=\"team-card-skill-abhiroop\">DEVELOPMENT</span><span class=\"team-card-skill-abhiroop\">PROBLEM SOLVING</span><span class=\"team-card-skill-abhiroop\">COLLABORATION</span><span class=\"team-card-skill-abhiroop\">AMITY UNIVERSITY</span></div><div style=\"font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:20px\">VIEW PROFILE →</div></a><style>\n        .team-card-aahana {\n          display: block;\n          border: 1px solid rgba(255,105,180,0.3);\n          background: rgba(255,105,180,0.07);\n          padding: 28px;\n          transition: box-shadow 0.2s;\n          position: relative;\n          text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .team-card-aahana:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(255,105,180,0.35); }\n        .team-card-skill-aahana {\n          font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px;\n          padding: 4px 10px; letter-spacing: 1px;\n          border: 1px solid rgba(255,105,180,0.3);\n          color: #ff69b4; background: rgba(255,105,180,0.07);\n        }\n      </style><a class=\"team-card-aahana\" href=\"/team/aahana\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #ff69b4, transparent)\"></div><div style=\"width:56px;height:56px;border:2px solid #ff69b4;background:rgba(255,105,180,0.07);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--display);font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#ff69b4;margin-bottom:20px;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,105,180,0.35)\">A</div><div style=\"font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:#ff69b4;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:8px\">FRIENDS // DESK HELPER PROJECT</div><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--display);font-size:18px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:6px;line-height:1.2\">AAHANA<!-- --> <span style=\"color:#ff69b4\">HAJARIWALA</span></h3><p style=\"font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;co